        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24713233/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24713233/" class="">第53页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/deviline/" class=" " title="Haldamir">Haldamir</a>
                (Gray cloak)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="24713233">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">政治，永远都不是一个可以讲道德的战场。
</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-02-21 00:42</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>政治，永远都不是一个可以讲道德的战场。
</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

